Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.25,0:00:02.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.83,0:00:05.62,Main,,0,0,0,,As I'm sure you know, summer vacation starts tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.70,0:00:07.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Try not to get into any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.62,0:00:14.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Summer vacation is gonna be awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.54,0:00:15.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.85,0:00:17.95,Main,,0,0,0,,We're thinking of going to the beach tomorrow, you in?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.04,0:00:19.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you know it, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:22.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I suddenly have a huge craving for watermelon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:23.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd eat some watermelon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:24.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Perfect! Let's get one for tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.04,0:00:25.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.04,0:02:07.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.16,0:02:08.50,Main,,0,0,0,,You excited?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.58,0:02:09.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:12.00,Main,,0,0,0,,It feels like I've been waiting for it forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.08,0:02:14.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Now I can play as much as I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.08,0:02:15.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm a free man!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.20,0:02:17.54,Main,,0,0,0,,You better not forget about your homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.62,0:02:19.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Knowing you, you'll put it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.37,0:02:21.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I bet you're thinking "play first, work later."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:23.08,Main,,0,0,0,,How'd you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:24.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Haha! So I was right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.91,0:02:25.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Well yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:28.70,Main,,0,0,0,,But the whole point of a break is to relax, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:31.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanna go to the pool, hit the\Nbeach, and go camping and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:34.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Man, I barely have enough time to do all that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:39.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I wish we could just have summer vacation forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.25,0:02:40.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.75,0:02:42.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I like going to school, too, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.37,0:02:44.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:49.15,Main,,0,0,0,,It's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.08,0:02:53.50,Main,,0,0,0,,No more of that for a while, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.41,0:02:55.55,Main,,0,0,0,,So hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.68,0:02:57.50,Main,,0,0,0,,But the breeze feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:02:59.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you go faster? This rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.83,0:03:02.41,Main,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't be saying that if you were pedaling!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:09.22,Main,,0,0,0,,It's hot out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:17.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Should we do what they were doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:18.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.16,0:03:20.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course, you'd have to be in the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,0:03:21.70,Main,,0,0,0,,No. We can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.79,0:03:24.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh. 'Cuz it'd be dangerous\Nwith cars driving by, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:26.41,Main,,0,0,0,,There are no cars around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:28.24,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not even a public road.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:29.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:30.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:32.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you embarrassed or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.62,0:03:34.33,Main,,0,0,0,,No! Of course I'm not embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.41,0:03:35.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.16,0:03:36.75,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't do it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.83,0:03:38.00,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.08,0:03:40.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Tandem riding is super easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.41,0:03:43.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I just don't think we should do it, 'cuz it's not safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:46.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the vacant lot, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.95,0:03:48.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:56.91,Main,,0,0,0,,If you can't do it, then you owe me a juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I hope you're not too thirsty,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.62,0:04:00.60,Main,,0,0,0,,because I got this, no sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:04.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:06.25,Main,,0,0,0,,That was just the practice run!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:07.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:11.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll take grape.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:13.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Could ya gimme a second?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:16.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it really this hard to ride with\Nsomeone sitting on the back of a bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.16,0:04:20.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Just checking, but you're not trying to\Nthrow us off balance on purpose, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.87,0:04:22.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:23.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:25.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm just sitting how I usually sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.83,0:04:27.08,Main,,0,0,0,,If we can't get it to work,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:28.95,Main,,0,0,0,,then it's gotta be your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:30.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:32.62,Main,,0,0,0,,...the last time I did this with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:35.49,Main,,0,0,0,,They didn't have any trouble peddling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:36.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:37.86,Main,,0,0,0,,That's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.45,0:04:40.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I take it they were a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:41.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.50,0:04:42.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Not a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.74,0:04:43.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:51.45,Main,,0,0,0,,One more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:53.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I think I've almost got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:56.75,Main,,0,0,0,,This time for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:57.58,Main,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.66,0:04:58.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Why do I feel so frustrated?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.74,0:05:01.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm just riding a bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:02.54,Main,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:03.62,Main,,0,0,0,,You're getting into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.70,0:05:04.79,Main,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:07.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I just don't wanna waste my hard earned money on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:08.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:10.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I just don't want to buy her a drink! That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:16.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:17.95,Main,,0,0,0,,We're moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:19.87,Main,,0,0,0,,By the way, Nishikata,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:22.58,Main,,0,0,0,,the last time I rode on the back of someone's bike,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.66,0:05:24.83,Main,,0,0,0,,it was my dad's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.91,0:05:26.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I think I was four at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.75,0:05:35.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:37.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Why, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:43.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:44.87,Main,,0,0,0,,That's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:48.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you not gonna get yourself a drink, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.33,0:05:49.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh. Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:52.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm, uhh, not thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:55.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't tell her I have no money to buy my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:57.04,Main,,0,0,0,,How would that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:05:59.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:04.75,Main,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.83,0:06:06.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.41,0:06:09.71,Main,,0,0,0,,She'd just call it an indirect\Nkiss again to get me to blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.41,0:06:12.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, I know you're thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:12.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:14.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I really don't want any.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:18.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Endure it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.37,0:06:21.41,Main,,0,0,0,,You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:22.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Endure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.83,0:06:27.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Drink this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.16,0:06:29.57,Main,,0,0,0,,We can't have you getting heatstroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:31.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I can have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:33.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:35.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Besides.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:37.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:39.75,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't want mine because it's an indirect kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:41.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:43.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Tha-That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:44.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm just not thirsty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:46.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.25,0:06:47.70,Main,,0,0,0,,But you'll drink yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.79,0:06:49.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, you already bought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:52.07,Main,,0,0,0,,It'd be a waste when it's this hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.95,0:06:56.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:01.62,Main,,0,0,0,,We won't be walking home from school for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:02.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.66,0:07:03.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Got that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:05.37,Main,,0,0,0,,We're on vacation, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:08.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.62,0:07:12.66,Main,,0,0,0,,How about starting tomorrow,\Nwe practice tandem riding here until noon?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:15.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:16.20,Main,,0,0,0,,But not on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:17.33,Main,,0,0,0,,That's what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:19.04,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll just ride here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:23.66,Main,,0,0,0,,If we're only ever gonna ride here,\Nthere's no point in practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.66,0:07:25.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:27.04,Main,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.12,0:07:28.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:30.83,Main,,0,0,0,,It starts tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:33.70,Main,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:35.66,Main,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.75,0:07:38.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, we should head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.16,0:07:42.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.45,0:07:43.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.70,0:07:44.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.62,0:07:46.40,Main,,0,0,0,,It'll be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.08,0:07:48.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:56.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Why'd it have to rain on our first day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:57.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:08:00.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Summer vacation's barely even started,\Nand my plans are already ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:02.75,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not like it's supposed to rain tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:05.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I wanted to go to the pool today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:07.70,Main,,0,0,0,,And I'm never getting that time back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,0:08:09.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Please stop crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.79,0:08:13.16,Main,,0,0,0,,You know we can't do anything about the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:15.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's just start our homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:16.25,Main,,0,0,0,,--Huh? --Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.33,0:08:17.95,Main,,0,0,0,,What's with those faces?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.04,0:08:20.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you two didn't bring yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:24.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I told you guys to bring your\Nhomework over since it's raining out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:26.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I figured I must have misheard you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:27.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:31.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Why do we get assigned homework during\Nsummer vacation in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.12,0:08:32.95,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a violation of human rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.04,0:08:34.87,Main,,0,0,0,,It's hardly a break with homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:36.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.33,0:08:39.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Dream all you want, we still have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.58,0:08:51.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Do me a personal favor,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.62,0:08:53.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Quit doing your homework and relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:58.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Seeing you do yours reminds me that I have to do\Nmine, and now I can't enjoy myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:08:59.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.25,0:09:00.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe you need the reminder!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:03.66,Main,,0,0,0,,It's only the first day still.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:06.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Just forget about school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:14.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Typical, from a person who will be crying\Nwith regret on August thirty-first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:15.44,Main,,0,0,0,,You're so stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.87,0:09:17.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Forget you. I'm gonna read manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:19.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:21.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:25.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yukari?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:27.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:28.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I got a great idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:30.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Can we write our book report on manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.45,0:09:32.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.41,0:09:35.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you two just go home already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:45.91,Main,,0,0,0,,It stopped raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:47.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.66,0:09:50.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, why exactly am I happy about that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:09:57.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishikata.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:05.45,Main,,0,0,0,,You're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:07.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we made a promise, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:09.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:13.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.29,0:10:14.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.29,0:10:15.33,Main,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.41,0:10:17.16,Main,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.25,0:10:18.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.29,0:10:20.12,Main,,0,0,0,,There are so many puddles here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:21.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, you know what they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.54,0:10:23.20,Main,,0,0,0,,When it rains, it pours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.29,0:10:26.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't recognize her for a second there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.08,0:10:29.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I've run into her\Na few times on our days off by chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.91,0:10:32.54,Main,,0,0,0,,but this is our first time meeting up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:34.66,Main,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.75,0:10:36.91,Main,,0,0,0,,This isn't like, a date, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:38.70,Main,,0,0,0,,No, obviously not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:41.37,Main,,0,0,0,,We're just here to practice tandem\Nriding, like we agreed to!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:42.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishikata?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.54,0:10:44.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?! What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:45.87,Main,,0,0,0,,You hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:46.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:48.79,Main,,0,0,0,,No. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:50.75,Main,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.83,0:10:53.25,Main,,0,0,0,,This place is in pretty bad riding condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:55.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.66,0:10:56.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:10:59.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I was planning to go out after we practiced today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:01.45,Main,,0,0,0,,No sense going back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.54,0:11:04.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you wanna hang out with me to kill some time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,0:11:05.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:07.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Is this a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.12,0:11:09.75,Main,,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.83,0:11:10.75,Main,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.83,0:11:12.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh. Yeah, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.87,0:11:15.62,Main,,0,0,0,,But let's go someplace where\Nthere aren't too many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:18.83,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no telling what our\Nclassmates would say if they saw us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.83,0:11:20.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.54,0:11:22.04,Main,,0,0,0,,How about...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.12,0:11:23.43,Main,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:27.79,Main,,0,0,0,,A test of courage?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:29.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Perfect for summer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:31.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be scarier if we did it at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:33.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Not by much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.41,0:11:35.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I heard it gets pitch black when you're in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.66,0:11:41.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Some say, there's a presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:42.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.58,0:11:43.20,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.29,0:11:44.33,Main,,0,0,0,,A presence?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:45.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, that's what I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:48.66,Main,,0,0,0,,This tunnel doesn't have any sharp turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.75,0:11:52.91,Main,,0,0,0,,But for some reason, a lot of cars ended\Nup crashing straight into the walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:55.50,Main,,0,0,0,,So they had to make a new road nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.54,0:12:02.79,Main,,0,0,0,,And since then, every night, without\Nfail, a bloodthirsty ghost appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:05.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Looking for cars to prey upon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:07.04,Main,,0,0,0,,But there's even more to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:08.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Rumor has it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:10.62,Main,,0,0,0,,People are spirited away here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.70,0:12:11.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Dozens.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.65,0:12:14.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe more have disappeared right in this very tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.83,0:12:17.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you going in?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:20.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Or are you chicken?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.04,0:12:22.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I am so not chicken!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.25,0:12:24.39,Main,,0,0,0,,It's the middle of the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.39,0:12:29.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Why would I be scared of going in some\Ndusty, stupid, old tunnel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:33.33,Main,,0,0,0,,It's way darker than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.29,0:12:39.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Why is the wind making such a weird noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:40.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.12,0:12:42.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Check out what's on the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.25,0:12:43.75,Main,,0,0,0,,A talisman?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.83,0:12:44.75,Main,,0,0,0,,For spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:46.16,Main,,0,0,0,,It keeps them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.25,0:12:47.70,Main,,0,0,0,,So clearly,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.79,0:12:50.66,Main,,0,0,0,,there must be something evil in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:55.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not surprised you're scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:55.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.81,0:12:56.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I was just shocked, that's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:57.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:13:00.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh, great; what is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.29,0:13:03.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.58,0:13:05.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder what this steel barrel is doing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.83,0:13:07.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.95,0:13:08.66,Main,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:10.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I vote you look inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.29,0:13:12.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:13.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.37,0:13:14.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Will you stop saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.04,0:13:16.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll look.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:18.41,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not that big of a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:34.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:42.04,Main,,0,0,0,,That's what I was really worried about!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.70,0:13:44.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Takagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.25,0:13:48.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Takagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.75,0:13:50.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Where'd you run off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:56.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Quit messing with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.08,0:14:00.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Didn't she mention something about being spirited away?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:02.62,Main,,0,0,0,,But that couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:03.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.04,0:14:05.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.91,0:14:07.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Takagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.87,0:14:17.41,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you freaking out for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:18.62,Main,,0,0,0,,It's just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.70,0:14:20.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Where'd you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.37,0:14:21.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.62,0:14:24.25,Main,,0,0,0,,You were looking for me just now, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.33,0:14:25.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:27.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Why would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.91,0:14:30.63,Main,,0,0,0,,So she lured me in here to jump-scare me a ton.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.91,0:14:32.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:34.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:37.00,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a big hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.08,0:14:39.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't you take a peek inside it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:42.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Like I'd fall for the same trick twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:43.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.38,0:14:45.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh no, I'm stuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.95,0:14:47.95,Main,,0,0,0,,My hand's stuck in the hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.04,0:14:49.37,Main,,0,0,0,,How do you like my acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:50.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I've been working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.54,0:14:52.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna freak you out so bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:54.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know what,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:56.08,Main,,0,0,0,,but it feels like something's\Npulling me from the other side!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:57.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Help me--!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:15:00.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Nishikata.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.91,0:15:03.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Did I scare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.66,0:15:04.25,Main,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:05.25,Main,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.33,0:15:06.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I dunno, I found it on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.58,0:15:10.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.37,0:15:12.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Glad your hand came loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:14.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:16.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I gotta find some way to get\Nher before we leave this tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:21.62,Main,,0,0,0,,As jumpy as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.58,0:15:24.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.83,0:15:26.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Some fresh air!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.25,0:15:27.41,Main,,0,0,0,,This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.50,0:15:29.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I couldn't find anything to get her back with.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:33.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Must be another couple on a date in the spooky tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.83,0:15:35.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't bother them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:36.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:38.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:42.20,Main,,0,0,0,,She called it a "date."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:44.41,Main,,0,0,0,,She doesn't know what she's talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:46.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:47.12,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:48.87,Main,,0,0,0,,You're blushing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.37,0:15:51.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Did you have fun back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:53.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Because I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.37,0:15:54.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.83,0:15:56.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.54,0:15:58.70,Main,,0,0,0,,It's almost noon, we should go back home soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:00.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.62,0:16:02.12,Main,,0,0,0,,What way are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:07.20,Main,,0,0,0,,You want to go back through there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.29,0:16:08.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.33,0:16:09.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.41,0:16:10.70,Main,,0,0,0,,When am I ever?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.79,0:16:20.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I met my quota for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:21.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:23.12,Main,,0,0,0,,It's summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:26.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Why do I still have just as\Nmany push-ups to do as normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.29,0:16:32.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, the consommé flavor is quite good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:33.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:35.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Your eyes are watering.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:36.50,Main,,0,0,0,,No, they're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.58,0:16:38.87,Main,,0,0,0,,And I know it's better than your kelp flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.95,0:16:40.33,Main,,0,0,0,,They both sound awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.41,0:16:43.87,Main,,0,0,0,,There are so many flavors to choose from.\NWhy would you pick those?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:46.41,Main,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't understand, miss watermelon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:49.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Take risks while you're still young, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:51.87,Main,,0,0,0,,That's some philosophy to apply to popsicles.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:55.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you two decide on\Nsubjects for the science project?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.08,0:16:56.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:57.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:16:58.54,Main,,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:00.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm still thinking, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:04.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Isn't there something easy I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:06.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Like, finish-in-a-day easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:08.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Just do actual research.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:10.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:12.00,Main,,0,0,0,,A dog observation diary?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:13.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah! Awesome idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.66,0:17:15.33,Main,,0,0,0,,That sounds super easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.41,0:17:18.04,Main,,0,0,0,,And dogs basically behave the same way every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:20.50,Main,,0,0,0,,So I can just copy the entries and change the dates!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:23.00,Main,,0,0,0,,If you're gonna lie, write it by hand at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:25.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Besides, dogs barely do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:28.08,Main,,0,0,0,,They wake up, bark for a walk, bark to be fed,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:29.95,Main,,0,0,0,,and sleep every chance they get.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.04,0:17:31.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe they'll wake up and bark for attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:34.25,Main,,0,0,0,,but then they'll just bark for food again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.33,0:17:36.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Why would anyone want to observe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:38.79,Main,,0,0,0,,You're such a stick in the mud, Yukari.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:40.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Well she is the class president.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:42.66,Main,,0,0,0,,It comes with the territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.75,0:17:44.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:45.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:49.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyway, have you two started to do your homework yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:53.00,Main,,0,0,0,,We've still got plenty of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.08,0:17:54.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.33,0:17:57.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Just so you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.25,0:17:59.04,Main,,0,0,0,,You're not copying mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:02.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Not even if I do your science project for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.44,0:18:03.25,Main,,0,0,0,,On a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.25,0:18:04.29,Main,,0,0,0,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.37,0:18:07.79,Main,,0,0,0,,You say this now, but you're gonna end\Nup sharing your answers with us anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.79,0:18:09.58,Main,,0,0,0,,She wants the class to get good grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.66,0:18:11.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.25,0:18:15.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should do an observation\Ndiary on their procrastination habits.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:21.91,Main,,0,0,0,,So hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:26.33,Main,,0,0,0,,This is the worst day of vacation yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:28.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:30.56,Main,,0,0,0,,First, I overslept.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:34.66,Main,,0,0,0,,And then I had a flat tire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:39.29,Main,,0,0,0,,But at least all this happened on a\Nday we're not practicing tandem riding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:41.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Takagi said she was going on a family vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.62,0:18:45.28,Main,,0,0,0,,When's she coming back from that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:49.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I was gonna stay home for a few hours and do\Nchores, so I could have the afternoon free,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.50,0:18:52.14,Main,,0,0,0,,but of course I was sent on a shopping trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:55.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Truly this is the darkest of vacations.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.45,0:18:57.93,Main,,0,0,0,,That kinda sounded poetic, I should write it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:02.39,Main,,0,0,0,,That looks like...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:06.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.84,0:19:08.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:11.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess she's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:14.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I might as well use this opportunity to follow her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.20,0:19:19.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe I can find a weakness to exploit in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.12,0:19:35.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.33,0:19:36.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Did she see me there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.04,0:19:39.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.33,0:19:42.12,Main,,0,0,0,,No, she did see me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:44.88,Main,,0,0,0,,But I can see her hat sticking out around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:47.70,Main,,0,0,0,,You think you're gonna surprise me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:49.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Not while I still may breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:51.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I should write that down, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.58,0:20:01.16,Main,,0,0,0,,She... She got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.25,0:20:02.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Going somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:02.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.95,0:20:04.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Just grocery shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.79,0:20:05.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:06.58,Main,,0,0,0,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.66,0:20:08.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I am too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:10.62,Main,,0,0,0,,We could take your bike, ride tandem?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:11.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.79,0:20:13.75,Main,,0,0,0,,We agreed no doing that in the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.37,0:20:16.54,Main,,0,0,0,,When did she find out I was following her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.62,0:20:17.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.41,0:20:18.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's walk together, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.66,0:20:21.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh no! I gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.37,0:20:25.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.41,0:20:29.54,Main,,0,0,0,,And the curse of today continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:31.37,Main,,0,0,0,,You're hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.45,0:20:34.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Nah. It's nothing. I'll just let it be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.16,0:20:35.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:37.03,Main,,0,0,0,,You should wash it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:47.66,Main,,0,0,0,,How embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.75,0:20:49.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Does your knee hurt that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.70,0:20:50.95,Main,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:55.79,Main,,0,0,0,,It's just that I was already having a bad\Nday, and now I got a cut, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.79,0:20:58.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm wallowing in how much this vacation sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:02.56,Main,,0,0,0,,And it's not like I can write about\Nmy misfortunes for my summer homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.91,0:21:03.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:05.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.04,0:21:07.37,Main,,0,0,0,,But it'll stain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:09.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, just take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:11.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:12.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:27.20,Main,,0,0,0,,That feels nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.79,0:21:30.88,Main,,0,0,0,,So you tried to catch me before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.41,0:21:33.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.00,0:21:36.20,Main,,0,0,0,,You should come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.29,0:21:38.16,Main,,0,0,0,,The cold water's really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.25,0:21:40.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh, No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:42.30,Main,,0,0,0,,You know you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.16,0:21:47.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Cooling you down?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.75,0:21:49.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.29,0:21:51.20,Main,,0,0,0,,You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:54.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I had a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.62,0:21:56.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Because I got to see someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.79,0:21:58.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.37,0:21:59.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.95,0:22:02.66,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll get your souvenir tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.58,0:22:04.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.24,0:22:07.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop that Takagi, the water's really cold!
